  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the world of trading used (or stolen) cars!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Got little money and nothing to lose? We were waiting for you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Used Cars Simulator</strong>, you’ll fix up cars, put them up for sale, grow your business in an old shed, drive around an abandoned city, drink beer, and wander the desert with a metal detector.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And it all starts when you meet a beautiful woman in a red dress at your favorite bar… Are you in?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>FIND A GOOD OFFER</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637940/extras/25a945a97906e52de7e8fcacf90123fc.poster.avif?t=1773913872\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637940/extras/25a945a97906e52de7e8fcacf90123fc.webm?t=1773913872\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637940/extras/25a945a97906e52de7e8fcacf90123fc.mp4?t=1773913872\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Used Cars Simulator</strong>, you'll learn how to make money by trading cars.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >First, find a good deal. Check the car’s condition, negotiate the price, and if everything looks good - just buy it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>FIX THE CAR</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637940/extras/1d3f6c598b4cdb19ab160785bd8c8864.poster.avif?t=1773913872\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637940/extras/1d3f6c598b4cdb19ab160785bd8c8864.webm?t=1773913872\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637940/extras/1d3f6c598b4cdb19ab160785bd8c8864.mp4?t=1773913872\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fix the dents, order and install missing parts, wash the car, repaint it, and put it up for sale. If it wasn’t yours, you’d probably want to buy it yourself!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>BE BAD</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637940/extras/ac9bf1ace70daad8ac4310f563862b91.poster.avif?t=1773913872\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637940/extras/ac9bf1ace70daad8ac4310f563862b91.webm?t=1773913872\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637940/extras/ac9bf1ace70daad8ac4310f563862b91.mp4?t=1773913872\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Used Cars Simulator,</strong> there are many ways to get cars. Are they all legal? Sure - as long as the cops don’t catch you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>HAVE FUN</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637940/extras/e0245694a16732a21b570f145122986d.poster.avif?t=1773913872\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637940/extras/e0245694a16732a21b570f145122986d.webm?t=1773913872\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637940/extras/e0245694a16732a21b570f145122986d.mp4?t=1773913872\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After work, have some fun - drift, jump, and compare your scores with other players on the leaderboards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>PROGRESS</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What’s coming in future updates? You tell us! Let us know which features we should add.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features of Used Cars Simulator:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅ Car Trading & Flipping</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅ Story & Quests</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅ Physics & Sandbox</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅ Illegal Activities</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅ Police Interactions</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅ World Exploration</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅ Upgrades & Economy</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the world of trading used (or stolen) cars!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Got little money and nothing to lose? We were waiting for you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Used Cars Simulator</strong>, you’ll fix up cars, put them up for sale, grow your business in an old shed, drive around an abandoned city, drink beer, and wander the desert with a metal detector.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And it all starts when you meet a beautiful woman in a red dress at your favorite bar… Are you in?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>FIND A GOOD OFFER</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637940/extras/25a945a97906e52de7e8fcacf90123fc.poster.avif?t=1773913872\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637940/extras/25a945a97906e52de7e8fcacf90123fc.webm?t=1773913872\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637940/extras/25a945a97906e52de7e8fcacf90123fc.mp4?t=1773913872\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Used Cars Simulator</strong>, you'll learn how to make money by trading cars.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >First, find a good deal. Check the car’s condition, negotiate the price, and if everything looks good - just buy it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>FIX THE CAR</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637940/extras/1d3f6c598b4cdb19ab160785bd8c8864.poster.avif?t=1773913872\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637940/extras/1d3f6c598b4cdb19ab160785bd8c8864.webm?t=1773913872\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637940/extras/1d3f6c598b4cdb19ab160785bd8c8864.mp4?t=1773913872\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fix the dents, order and install missing parts, wash the car, repaint it, and put it up for sale. If it wasn’t yours, you’d probably want to buy it yourself!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>BE BAD</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637940/extras/ac9bf1ace70daad8ac4310f563862b91.poster.avif?t=1773913872\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637940/extras/ac9bf1ace70daad8ac4310f563862b91.webm?t=1773913872\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637940/extras/ac9bf1ace70daad8ac4310f563862b91.mp4?t=1773913872\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Used Cars Simulator,</strong> there are many ways to get cars. Are they all legal? Sure - as long as the cops don’t catch you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>HAVE FUN</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637940/extras/e0245694a16732a21b570f145122986d.poster.avif?t=1773913872\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637940/extras/e0245694a16732a21b570f145122986d.webm?t=1773913872\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2637940/extras/e0245694a16732a21b570f145122986d.mp4?t=1773913872\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After work, have some fun - drift, jump, and compare your scores with other players on the leaderboards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>PROGRESS</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What’s coming in future updates? You tell us! Let us know which features we should add.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features of Used Cars Simulator:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅ Car Trading & Flipping</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅ Story & Quests</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅ Physics & Sandbox</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅ Illegal Activities</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅ Police Interactions</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅ World Exploration</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅ Upgrades & Economy</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
